import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Button, Grid, Paper, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Divider } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <Container sx={{ py: 4 }}>
            <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom align="center">
                Welcome to Uplift
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6" paragraph align="center">
                Your go-to platform for connecting with mental health professionals and exploring valuable articles.
            </Typography>
            
            {/* Hero Section */}
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', mb: 4 }}>
                <Paper sx={{ p: 2, textAlign: 'center', maxWidth: 600, width: '100%' }}>
                    <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                        Discover a path to better mental health
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        Our platform provides easy access to licensed psychologists, psychiatrists, and a wealth of mental health resources. Start your journey with us today.
                    </Typography>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/articles">Explore Articles</Button>
                        <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" component={Link} to="/doctors">Find a Doctor</Button>
                    </Box>
                </Paper>
            </Box>

            {/* Features Section */}
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom align="center">
                Our Features
            </Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia
                            component="img"
                            height="140"
                            image="/images/articles.jpg" // Replace with your image path
                            alt="Explore Articles"
                        />
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography variant="h6">Explore Articles</Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                                Read articles written by experts to better understand and manage your mental health.
                            </Typography>
                            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/articles" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                                Read Articles
                            </Button>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia
                            component="img"
                            height="140"
                            image="/images" // Replace with your image path
                            alt="Find a Doctor"
                        />
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography variant="h6">Find a Doctor</Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                                Connect with licensed mental health professionals who can offer personalized support.
                            </Typography>
                            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/doctors" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                                Find a Doctor
                            </Button>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia
                            component="img"
                            height="140"
                            image="/images/community.jpg" // Replace with your image path
                            alt="Join the Community"
                        />
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography variant="h6">Join the Community</Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                                Engage in discussions with peers and experts to share experiences and advice.
                            </Typography>
                            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/community" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                                Join Community
                            </Button>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>

            <Divider sx={{ my: 4 }} />

            {/* Call to Action */}
            <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                    Ready to make a change?
                </Typography>
                <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" component={Link} to="/signup">
                    Sign Up Now
                </Button>
            </Box>
        </Container>
    );
};

export default Home;
